text: "It's Raining Again" is a 1982 song by English rock band Supertramp and taken from their 7th studio album ...Famous Last Words.... It went to number 1 in France, number 2 in Switzerland, number 3 in Germany, number 4 in Canada, number 6 in the Netherlands, Norway and South Africa, number 7 in Austria and number 11 in Australia and the United States. ==Track listings== ===7-inch vinyl=== == References == Category:1982 songs Category:Supertramp songs Category:Pop rock songs
title: It's Raining Again
